steps.name: New User Setup: Free User Sign up
Free user sign up API call
New User Setup: Free User Email Confirmation via Database
New User Setup: Free User Login
New User Setup: Upgrade Free User to Business
Click the Settings on the Side Menu
Click on the Billing option in the side menu
Click "No,thanks" button on the One Time Special Offer Modal
A toast message with the text "Plan has been successfully changed." is visible and hidden then
Click the "Documents" item on the left SideMenu
Check two random documents and collect their titles
Click on the "Delete" tab in the Select options dropdown menu
Click on the "Yes, Delete" button in the modal window
Click the "Trash" in the Documents SideMenu
Verify documents in trash have correct titles "CSV.csv,todoList.xlsx"
Click "Empty trash" button on the confirmation window
Click the "Documents" item on the left SideMenu
Verify that there is only one undeleted document with correct title "openHouse.pdf"
